onclick Event in javascript

function is a set of statements written in block that can be called by function name when it is required;

Creating functions in javascript:
	function in javascript is created using function keyword.
	Syntax:
		function funName()
		{
			//Statements of functions goes here
		}
	Example:
		function fnClick()
		{
			alert("Hi,How are you?");
		}

		Here alert renders an alert box on the webpage.

	Inbuilt function isNaN(parameter is the value you want to check) is a method that is used to check whether the enetered value is number or not.
